    <para id="id1169040117729"/>
    <para id="id1169038913924"/>
    <para id="id1169039889589">Activity 3: To examine how topsoil is formed</para>
    <para id="id1169041903671">[LO 2.2]</para>
    <para id="id1169039871437"> Study the sketches below and then answer the questions that follow: </para>
